anki: anki (friendly, intelligent flashcards)
anki:
anki: Anki is a program which makes remembering things easy. Because it is
anki: a lot more efficient than traditional study methods, you can either
anki: greatly decrease your time spent studying, or greatly increase the
anki: amount you learn. Anyone who needs to remember things in their daily
anki: life can benefit from Anki. Since it is content-agnostic and supports
anki: images, audio, video and scientificic markup, the possibilities are
anki: endless.
anki:
anki: Package created by Niki Kovacs <info@microlinux.fr>
